---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Sidebar from "../components/Sidebar.astro";
---

<Layout title="关于">
  <div id="app" class="main flex flex-col px-4 lg:flex-row">
    <Sidebar />
    <div
      class="content-wrapper post-detail animated fadeIn pt-32 lg:w-3/4 lg:p-8"
      :class="{ 'is-second': menuVisible }"
    >
      <h1 class="break-all text-3xl font-bold">关于</h1>

      <div class="my-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 lg:flex-row lg:gap-8">
        <img
          class="size-32 rounded-full object-cover shadow-md lg:size-40"
          src="/assets/avatar.jpg"
          alt="头像"
          width="160"
          height="160"
        />
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">LythoX</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-base-content/70">
            保持微笑
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="my-8 border-base-content/10" />

      <div class="tailwind-typography markdown-body overflow-hidden">
        <h2>关于本站</h2>
        <p>
          这是一个基于 <strong>Astro</strong> 搭建的个人博客，使用了 <strong>Walker</strong> 主题的设计风格。
          Walker 是一款漂亮、简洁、优雅的博客主题，由 EryouHao 设计，最初为 Gridea 开发，后由 Halo 团队移植到 Halo 平台。
        </p>

        <h2>技术栈</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>框架：</strong>Astro</li>
          <li><strong>样式：</strong>Tailwind CSS + daisyUI</li>
          <li><strong>交互：</strong>Alpine.js</li>
          <li><strong>部署：</strong>GitHub Pages</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>联系我</h2>
        <p>
          <a href="https://github.com/LythoX0" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-base-content/70 hover:text-base-content">
            <i class="i-ri-github-line inline-block text-xl"></i>
            GitHub
          </a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
